{"tid":1523782,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵認左默許黑警入車廂恐襲","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T18:56:40.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7248aaece21c063be7781515608ec3be31a50bc8","tid":1523782,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:10:36.000Z","msg":"港鐵多個車站，晚上都有大批警員進入站內，向市民搜身、拘捕，以及在車廂內向乘客揮動警棍的情況，有市民受傷。<br />\n<br />\n在港鐵的傳媒即時通訊群組內，有傳媒問為何警方進入車站拘捕示威者，而港鐵封閉太子站出口，事前是否已和警方商討安排，港鐵代表回應指，因為站內發生乘客衝突，對其他乘客和員工的安全帶來威脅，車站啓動了疏散程序；又指得悉有乘客衝突後報警求助，<span style=\"color: red;\">警方有權進入車站範圍，包括車廂採取執法行動。</span>"},{"pid":"a81768e6f77c7a078f4ec83331be56e81643b105","tid":1523782,"uid":95487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試下找不同？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5402fd6c0d54556805a33107938e171442a98cd","tid":1523782,"uid":102145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:12:18.000Z","msg":"直播見到有黑警係控制室內"},{"pid":"5cdbfe74d759c5f7da1585715e748dc068088c09","tid":1523782,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"黨鐵姓黨"},{"pid":"c3caf2c8846c245793c6f0896dbff964c7a92560","tid":1523782,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DkbOEff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDkbOEff.jpg&h=24262b87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mL6KW1X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmL6KW1X.jpg&h